</figure>

<p>For the smoke I used an emitter with particles rendered as spheres, textured with the same ‚Äútoonish‚Äù custom material. I also used a blend texture on particles to animate the scale of these spheres along their lifetime. Added buoyancy, wind, turbulence and tweaked it quite a lot.</p>

<p>The project was initially to model a small flying city and have this boat float around‚Ä¶ That may be for another time.</p>
